#: ../../topics/jobs/schedule.rst:6
msgid "Salt Scheduling"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topics/jobs/schedule.rst:8
msgid ""
"In Salt versions greater than 0.12.0, the scheduling system allows "
"incremental executions on minions or the master. The schedule system exposes"
" the execution of any execution function on minions or any runner on the "
"master."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topics/jobs/schedule.rst:12
msgid ""
"To set up the scheduler on the master add the schedule option to the master "
"config file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topics/jobs/schedule.rst:15
msgid ""
"To set up the scheduler on the minion add the schedule option to the minion "
"config file or to the minion's pillar."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topics/jobs/schedule.rst:20
msgid ""
"The scheduler executes different functions on the master and minions. When "
"running on the master the functions reference runner functions, when running"
" on the minion the functions specify execution functions."
msgstr ""

